summary:
My fields of professional interest and experience are:

Project management.
Knowledge & experience transfer and its risks.
Conditioning and human bias in planning & decision making.
Impact and value of information in decision making.
Uncertainty analysis & quantification.
Risk analysis.
Risk management.
Well planning.
Geophysics.
Geology.
Seismic-to-well ties.
Seismic interpretation.
Seismic depth conversion.
Seismic processing.
Seismic survey design.
Applied physics.
Numerical analysis.
Multi-resolution/time-frequency/wavelet analysis in science & engineering.
Best basis selection.
Stochastic analysis.
Model selection principles.
